</section><section id="vendors" class="panel admin-panel"><h2>업체 관리</h2>
<div class="vendor-summary-grid" id="vendorSummaryGrid">
  <button type="button" data-vendor-card="all"><b>전체 업체</b><strong data-vendor-summary="total">0</strong></button>
  <button type="button" data-vendor-card="active"><b>정상노출</b><strong data-vendor-summary="active">0</strong></button>
  <button type="button" data-vendor-card="pending"><b>승인·검수중</b><strong data-vendor-summary="pending">0</strong></button>
  <button type="button" data-vendor-card="inactive"><b>숨김/만료</b><strong data-vendor-summary="hiddenOrExpired">0</strong></button>
  <button type="button" data-vendor-card="expiring"><b>7일 내 만료</b><strong data-vendor-summary="expiring">0</strong></button>
</div>
<p class="vendor-filter-note">업체목록은 광고상태, 노출상태, 만기상태를 기준으로 빠르게 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
<div class="vendor-toolbar">
  <button type="button" id="openVendorCreateModal" class="vendor-add-open">업체 등록</button>
</div>

<div id="vendorModal" class="vendor-modal">
  <div class="vendor-modal-box">
    <div class="vendor-modal-head">
      <h3 id="vendorModalTitle">업체 등록</h3>
      <button type="button" id="closeVendorModal" class="vendor-modal-close">닫기</button>
    </div>
<form id="vendorForm" method="post" action="/admin/vendor" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <input type="hidden" name="id">

  <div class="vendor-form-box">
    <h3>기본정보</h3>
    <div class="vendor-form-grid">
      <input name="name" placeholder="업체명" required>
      <select name="category" required><% (settings?.categories||[]).forEach(x=>{%><option value="<%=x%>"><%=x%></option><%})%></select>
      <select name="region" required><% (settings?.regions||[]).forEach(x=>{%><option value="<%=x%>"><%=x%></option><%})%></select>
      <input name="phone" placeholder="연락처">
      <input name="kakao_url" placeholder="카카오톡 문의 링크">
      <input name="tags" placeholder="태그">
    </div>
    <p class="vendor-form-help">업체명, 업종, 지역은 메인페이지 검색과 목록 노출에 사용됩니다. 관리자가 먼저 업체를 선등록한 뒤 회원관리에서 가입한 아이디와 연결할 수 있습니다.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="vendor-form-box">
    <h3>영업 / 소개</h3>
    <div class="vendor-form-grid two">
      <input name="business_hours" placeholder="영업시간">
      <textarea name="description" placeholder="업체소개"></textarea>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="vendor-form-box">
    <h3>광고 / 노출 설정</h3>
    <div class="vendor-form-grid">
      <select name="status"><option value="pending">검수중</option><option value="active">노출</option><option value="hidden">숨김</option><option value="expired">만료</option></select>
      <select name="ad_type"><option value="none">없음</option><option value="general">일반광고</option><option value="recommended">추천광고</option></select>
      <input name="expire_at" type="date" placeholder="광고/배너 만기일">
